00:00:11,669 --> 00:00:21,664
♪In ancient times, a meteor fell♪

2
00:00:22,528 --> 00:00:29,920
♪Scorching Nanba Weald into land bare♪

3
00:00:30,336 --> 00:00:39,993
♪From Turquoise Land beneath the sun♪

4
00:00:41,088 --> 00:00:52,256
♪The evil Earth Fiends were born♪

5
00:00:55,168 --> 00:00:58,400
♪Marching in South Mountain's domain♪

6
00:00:58,400 --> 00:01:01,248
♪Sworn warriors raged for glory's gain♪

7
00:01:01,248 --> 00:01:03,328
♪Renamed guardians hold Yanguan true♪

8
00:01:03,328 --> 00:01:06,656
♪Peace in all lands, a priceless boon♪

9
00:01:12,224 --> 00:01:15,264
♪Seven hounds, two whips, one blade♪

10
00:01:15,264 --> 00:01:18,048
♪In rout and flight,
Earth Fiends escape♪

11
00:01:18,048 --> 00:01:20,839
♪Golden Gate seals fast♪

12
00:01:20,872 --> 00:01:25,243
♪South Mountain Hunters
on the righteous path♪

13
00:01:26,752 --> 00:01:37,024
♪South Mountain Hunters
on the righteous path♪

14
00:01:37,024 --> 00:01:41,216
=Love on the Turquoise Land=

15
00:01:41,216 --> 00:01:44,000
(This story is a work of fiction)

16
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:46,960
=Episode 5=

17
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:54,792
(Yan Tuo)

18
00:02:58,088 --> 00:03:01,828
(Yan Tuo, General Manager
of Roadsound Group)

19
00:03:04,072 --> 00:03:05,672
(Legal Representative, Lin Xirou)

20
00:03:08,584 --> 00:03:10,280
(Mr. Lu)

21
00:03:12,652 --> 00:03:14,611
Could you stop rushing me?

22
00:03:15,932 --> 00:03:17,092
The world has changed.

23
00:03:17,411 --> 00:03:19,372
Aesthetic tastes
are growing more unpredictable.

24
00:03:20,252 --> 00:03:21,411
What are you talking about?

25
00:03:22,252 --> 00:03:23,652
Your unmarketable new creation

26
00:03:23,691 --> 00:03:24,851
caught someone's eye.

27
00:03:25,332 --> 00:03:26,131
Really?

28
00:03:27,932 --> 00:03:28,812
I told him

29
00:03:29,131 --> 00:03:29,972
only drafts exist

30
00:03:29,972 --> 00:03:31,291
and the final product isn't done.

31
00:03:31,932 --> 00:03:32,652
Yet he insisted

32
00:03:32,972 --> 00:03:34,812
it's okay and he'd wait.

33
00:03:36,972 --> 00:03:38,212
Don't joke with me.

34
00:03:38,571 --> 00:03:39,652
Not sure if it's a joke.

35
00:03:40,052 --> 00:03:41,611
He prepaid for three pieces outright.

36
00:03:41,972 --> 00:03:42,772
He only wants

37
00:03:42,932 --> 00:03:43,972
to meet you

38
00:03:44,291 --> 00:03:45,372
and discuss art in person.

39
00:03:46,052 --> 00:03:46,972
Who is he?

40
00:03:47,332 --> 00:03:50,212
We can't pry about his background.

41
00:03:50,571 --> 00:03:52,212
Anyway, he's declared

42
00:03:52,652 --> 00:03:54,291
he'll buy whatever you produce.

43
00:03:54,972 --> 00:03:56,731
See? The world has changed.

44
00:04:22,652 --> 00:04:24,252
Are you sure nothing is wrong with him?

45
00:04:24,451 --> 00:04:25,851
A decent business owner.

46
00:04:26,372 --> 00:04:28,611
He started from scratch
through honest work.

47
00:04:28,812 --> 00:04:30,731
Since when do decent people
meet in cemeteries?

48
00:04:30,932 --> 00:04:32,492
It's why he's remarkable.

49
00:04:32,772 --> 00:04:33,451
Think about it.

50
00:04:33,652 --> 00:04:35,731
No invite to dinner
avoids dietary preferences.

51
00:04:35,932 --> 00:04:37,812
No invite to drinks
prevent seeming frivolous.

52
00:04:38,332 --> 00:04:40,972
No office meet avoids formal stiffness.

53
00:04:40,972 --> 00:04:41,812
No gallery meeting

54
00:04:41,851 --> 00:04:44,372
presumes you've outgrown such spaces.

55
00:04:44,492 --> 00:04:47,411
Which place has serene
yet meaningful setting

56
00:04:47,411 --> 00:04:48,812
suitable for discussing art freely

57
00:04:48,812 --> 00:04:50,372
and contemplating life deeply?

58
00:04:50,372 --> 00:04:51,851
Hotel executive lounge?

59
00:04:51,851 --> 00:04:52,731
Too pedestrian.

60
00:04:53,212 --> 00:04:54,372
Can a lounge allow you

61
00:04:54,372 --> 00:04:55,492
to explore life's essence,

62
00:04:55,891 --> 00:04:57,532
human destiny,

63
00:04:57,691 --> 00:04:59,812
or the end of life?

64
00:05:00,891 --> 00:05:01,812
I need to go.

65
00:05:02,171 --> 00:05:03,012
I see him.

66
00:05:09,772 --> 00:05:11,132
Is this how you treat clients?

67
00:05:12,572 --> 00:05:13,652
I'll require a refund.

68
00:05:13,931 --> 00:05:15,731
No need. I won't sell it to you.

69
00:05:15,931 --> 00:05:17,811
Your work is about rebirth, right?

70
00:05:20,572 --> 00:05:21,371
Madman.

71
00:05:26,692 --> 00:05:27,931
Though newly created

72
00:05:28,212 --> 00:05:29,291
with limited impact,

73
00:05:30,012 --> 00:05:31,251
I've read critiques

74
00:05:31,972 --> 00:05:33,291
that mostly interpret your work

75
00:05:33,611 --> 00:05:37,212
as depicting suffocation and confinement

76
00:05:38,051 --> 00:05:39,652
and conveying dark emotions.

77
00:05:41,692 --> 00:05:42,652
If you continue,

78
00:05:42,652 --> 00:05:44,332
you'll expose your ignorance.

79
00:05:48,491 --> 00:05:49,452
Whenever I come here,

80
00:05:50,132 --> 00:05:52,212
I don't feel death or fear.

81
00:05:53,491 --> 00:05:54,572
Your sculptures

82
00:05:54,652 --> 00:05:55,411
inexplicably

83
00:05:55,411 --> 00:05:56,611
don't oppress me.

84
00:05:57,291 --> 00:05:58,892
They evoke childbirth's struggle.

85
00:05:59,332 --> 00:06:01,692
Of course, it's agonizing

86
00:06:02,092 --> 00:06:03,371
for the mother and child,

87
00:06:04,171 --> 00:06:05,012
yet the miracle

88
00:06:05,012 --> 00:06:06,731
of new life emerging

89
00:06:07,132 --> 00:06:08,332
is the ultimate hope.

90
00:06:08,972 --> 00:06:09,491
So I believe

91
00:06:09,491 --> 00:06:10,772
you're fundamentally optimistic.

92
00:06:11,611 --> 00:06:13,452
True, I'm no art expert,

93
00:06:13,731 --> 00:06:14,772
but I'm not pretending.

94
00:06:14,892 --> 00:06:16,411
I genuinely admire your work.

95
00:06:20,772 --> 00:06:22,332
Let me share my interpretation.

96
00:06:22,332 --> 00:06:23,332
I'm all ears.

97
00:06:25,132 --> 00:06:26,332
Outsiders see

98
00:06:26,491 --> 00:06:27,811
a pampered heir

99
00:06:27,972 --> 00:06:29,371
living carefree.

100
00:06:29,772 --> 00:06:31,931
Even you've bought into this facade,

101
00:06:32,092 --> 00:06:32,731
trapped in

102
00:06:32,731 --> 00:06:34,892
an identity and fate you despise.

103
00:06:35,652 --> 00:06:37,452
If you truly appreciated my art,

104
00:06:38,092 --> 00:06:39,452
you'd recognize

105
00:06:39,491 --> 00:06:41,332
the dark emotions, such as suffocation

106
00:06:41,332 --> 00:06:42,452
and confinement

107
00:06:43,411 --> 00:06:44,851
that mirror your reality,

108
00:06:45,811 --> 00:06:46,972
instead of standing

109
00:06:47,132 --> 00:06:48,051
in front of me,

110
00:06:48,171 --> 00:06:49,772
spouting empty praise.

111
00:06:54,572 --> 00:06:56,051
Surprising depth of understanding

112
00:06:56,291 --> 00:06:57,851
for new acquaintances like us.

113
00:06:58,892 --> 00:07:01,452
I have no interest in understanding
a reckless madman

114
00:07:01,452 --> 00:07:02,931
who'd drown others with him in a car.

115
00:07:03,892 --> 00:07:05,452
My apologies. I acted rashly.

116
00:07:05,972 --> 00:07:07,772
I just wanted calm dialogue

117
00:07:07,772 --> 00:07:09,012
and honest communication.

118
00:07:09,411 --> 00:07:10,171
If you still think

119
00:07:10,171 --> 00:07:11,532
I'm mad after hearing me out,

120
00:07:12,491 --> 00:07:13,532
I'll put a stop to it.

121
00:07:13,532 --> 00:07:14,532
No more bothering.

122
00:07:22,772 --> 00:07:23,611
I'm not sure

123
00:07:23,611 --> 00:07:24,892
what you gain from being here.

124
00:07:25,772 --> 00:07:27,212
But this place makes me uneasy.

125
00:07:27,411 --> 00:07:28,132
Get to the point.

126
00:07:30,411 --> 00:07:33,332
I invited you here
to show you a piece of work.

127
00:07:35,212 --> 00:07:35,731
Work?

128
00:07:36,371 --> 00:07:37,012
A tombstone.

129
00:07:46,532 --> 00:07:47,411
A woman

130
00:07:48,611 --> 00:07:49,931
ruined my family.

131
00:07:51,012 --> 00:07:52,572
(Lin Xirou)
She even stole my mother's name.

132
00:07:53,572 --> 00:07:54,332
Lin Xirou is now

133
00:07:55,772 --> 00:07:57,652
in charge of the entire Roadsound Group,

134
00:07:57,652 --> 00:07:58,731
living carefree.

135
00:08:00,291 --> 00:08:03,012
This tombstone was erected for my mother

136
00:08:03,611 --> 00:08:04,972
and will also eventually be hers.

137
00:08:05,772 --> 00:08:08,291
Are you saying your biological mother
was named Lin Xirou,

138
00:08:09,092 --> 00:08:12,371
and the current Lin Xirou
of Roadsound Group

139
00:08:13,092 --> 00:08:14,491
is the one who killed her?

140
00:08:31,692 --> 00:08:32,892
I got you.

141
00:08:33,692 --> 00:08:34,411
Wait a bit longer.

142
00:08:34,532 --> 00:08:35,572
Dad will be home soon.

143
00:08:37,212 --> 00:08:37,811
Tuo.

144
00:08:38,371 --> 00:08:39,572
Dad.

145
00:08:40,291 --> 00:08:41,132
Sorry for being late.

146
00:08:41,371 --> 00:08:42,171
Here.

147
00:08:42,332 --> 00:08:44,371
Happy birthday.

148
00:08:44,371 --> 00:08:46,012
Such a beautiful toy car.

149
00:08:46,012 --> 00:08:46,972
Do you like it?

150
00:08:46,972 --> 00:08:48,851
Yes, I love it.

151
00:08:48,851 --> 00:08:51,051
Who is she?

152
00:08:52,692 --> 00:08:53,371
Honey,

153
00:08:54,532 --> 00:08:55,972
this is Li Ergou's sister,

154
00:08:56,132 --> 00:08:57,772
Shuangxiu. Li Shuangxiu.

155
00:08:59,332 --> 00:09:01,012
Since the baby you're carrying develops,

156
00:09:01,051 --> 00:09:02,772
and there's so much housework,

157
00:09:02,892 --> 00:09:04,731
Shuangxiu will stay here from now on.

158
00:09:04,851 --> 00:09:06,212
Order her around for chores

159
00:09:06,332 --> 00:09:07,892
like she's one of our family.

160
00:09:07,892 --> 00:09:09,532
Let me show you the place.

161
00:09:10,851 --> 00:09:13,171
You're about to give birth
and you're still doing chores.

162
00:09:13,171 --> 00:09:14,772
Dashan went to pick Tuo up from school.

163
00:09:14,931 --> 00:09:16,171
I'll go meet them halfway.

164
00:09:55,011 --> 00:09:55,731
Tuo,

165
00:09:57,812 --> 00:09:59,972
I have something very important to do.

166
00:10:01,011 --> 00:10:02,771
Be good and wait here, okay?

167
00:10:23,731 --> 00:10:27,131
Tuo, you may call me
Ms. Lin from now on.

168
00:10:27,812 --> 00:10:28,812
Ms. Lin.

169
00:10:34,491 --> 00:10:35,812
My full name is Lin Xirou.

170
00:10:50,851 --> 00:10:51,771
After that,

171
00:10:52,212 --> 00:10:53,251
she became

172
00:10:53,251 --> 00:10:54,692
the lady of our household.

173
00:10:57,812 --> 00:10:59,371
As a kid, I was clueless.

174
00:10:59,692 --> 00:11:00,771
For years,

175
00:11:00,771 --> 00:11:02,491
I had genuinely considered
her my family.

176
00:11:06,011 --> 00:11:07,371
After I eventually found

177
00:11:07,371 --> 00:11:08,651
my mother's diary,

178
00:11:08,771 --> 00:11:09,611
I realized...

179
00:11:14,212 --> 00:11:15,412
Why are you telling me this?

180
00:11:17,052 --> 00:11:17,972
Gou Ya

181
00:11:18,572 --> 00:11:20,452
was sent to the welfare home
by Lin Xirou.

182
00:11:21,692 --> 00:11:23,092
If he's truly an Earth Fiend,

183
00:11:24,251 --> 00:11:25,972
then Lin Xirou must control the key

184
00:11:26,052 --> 00:11:27,891
to transforming Earth Fiends
into human form.

185
00:11:29,292 --> 00:11:30,452
What else do you know?

186
00:11:30,812 --> 00:11:33,172
I've looked for a long time.
But she's too cautious.

187
00:11:34,292 --> 00:11:35,491
She has guarded against me.

188
00:11:36,292 --> 00:11:37,172
I found nothing.

189
00:11:37,812 --> 00:11:39,412
But now that Gou Ya is in trouble

190
00:11:39,932 --> 00:11:40,851
and I've met you

191
00:11:41,011 --> 00:11:42,172
and your organization,

192
00:11:42,771 --> 00:11:43,851
it gives me hope.

193
00:11:44,851 --> 00:11:45,972
I just want to know

194
00:11:45,972 --> 00:11:47,092
what I should do

195
00:11:47,371 --> 00:11:49,092
(Lin Xirou)
to avenge my mother.

196
00:11:50,651 --> 00:11:52,011
First, you need to find out

197
00:11:52,212 --> 00:11:53,572
exactly what Lin Xirou is.

198
00:11:53,891 --> 00:11:55,131
I don't care what she is.

199
00:11:56,891 --> 00:11:58,292
But I'm certain

200
00:11:58,531 --> 00:12:00,292
her connection
to Earth Fiends is unusual.

201
00:12:01,651 --> 00:12:02,851
If you truly oppose

202
00:12:02,851 --> 00:12:03,731
the Earth Fiends,

203
00:12:04,011 --> 00:12:04,771
working with me

204
00:12:05,371 --> 00:12:06,731
is a golden opportunity.

205
00:12:08,052 --> 00:12:10,731
You said it you considered
her your family.

206
00:12:10,891 --> 00:12:12,052
And she raised you.

207
00:12:13,011 --> 00:12:14,611
Do you think I'll take such a risk

208
00:12:14,731 --> 00:12:15,692
by working with you?

209
00:12:16,172 --> 00:12:18,292
If a hunter teams up with a wolf cub,

210
00:12:18,332 --> 00:12:19,972
they could destroy the entire wolf den.

211
00:12:19,972 --> 00:12:21,131
Isn't that worth the gamble?

212
00:12:21,332 --> 00:12:22,771
Don't flatter yourself as a wolf.

213
00:12:23,212 --> 00:12:25,332
You could be the snake
in the farmer's story.

214
00:12:28,371 --> 00:12:28,851
Fine.

215
00:12:30,692 --> 00:12:33,131
I know you're not afraid
of snakes or wolves.

216
00:12:35,011 --> 00:12:36,572
But you're afraid of water.

217
00:12:38,092 --> 00:12:40,251
I also know your home address
and workplace.

218
00:12:40,412 --> 00:12:41,932
Even your artistic philosophy.

219
00:12:42,692 --> 00:12:43,972
Driving a car into water

220
00:12:44,611 --> 00:12:45,572
was me going too far.

221
00:12:46,092 --> 00:12:47,412
But I can't promise

222
00:12:47,412 --> 00:12:48,812
I won't do it again.

223
00:12:55,212 --> 00:12:57,011
You're truly something.

224
00:12:57,771 --> 00:12:59,651
How rare to hear you say something kind.

225
00:13:00,491 --> 00:13:01,412
What do you mean?

226
00:13:03,052 --> 00:13:04,891
After hearing your life story earlier,

227
00:13:05,212 --> 00:13:06,172
I genuinely felt

228
00:13:06,172 --> 00:13:07,851
a slight sense of empathy.

229
00:13:08,251 --> 00:13:09,172
I even forgot about

230
00:13:09,172 --> 00:13:10,251
our past unpleasantness.

231
00:13:11,011 --> 00:13:11,932
But just now

232
00:13:12,011 --> 00:13:13,212
your words

233
00:13:13,491 --> 00:13:15,531
revived my disgust toward you.

234
00:13:16,251 --> 00:13:17,412
You have a way with people.

235
00:13:18,771 --> 00:13:19,891
If that's the case,

236
00:13:20,092 --> 00:13:21,651
your being immune to all persuasion

237
00:13:21,651 --> 00:13:22,812
and your sarcastic skills

238
00:13:22,812 --> 00:13:23,972
are thoroughly impressive.

239
00:13:24,812 --> 00:13:26,092
A truly dedicated

240
00:13:26,092 --> 00:13:27,572
and virtuous artist.

241
00:13:31,972 --> 00:13:32,572
Come with me.

242
00:13:33,172 --> 00:13:33,851
To where?

243
00:13:34,851 --> 00:13:36,491
I'll show you a sculpture.

244
00:14:00,078 --> 00:14:04,332
(Temple of the Righteous Lord)

245
00:14:04,332 --> 00:14:05,452
In ancient times,

246
00:14:06,052 --> 00:14:09,131
a meteor fell
into South Mountain's ancient woods.

247
00:14:10,052 --> 00:14:11,371
The meteor melted into the earth,

248
00:14:11,611 --> 00:14:12,771
turning the soil turquoise.

249
00:14:13,692 --> 00:14:17,212
Plants and animals mutated,
and strange occurrences multiplied.

250
00:14:18,092 --> 00:14:21,611
Then a type of light-fearing,

251
00:14:22,572 --> 00:14:23,651
carnivorous savage beasts

252
00:14:23,651 --> 00:14:25,172
started roaming South Mountain.

253
00:14:26,371 --> 00:14:27,812
The locals

254
00:14:27,932 --> 00:14:29,812
named those beasts Earth Fiends.

255
00:14:30,371 --> 00:14:32,731
Earth Fiends were brutal killers.

256
00:14:32,812 --> 00:14:34,131
People suffered terribly.

257
00:14:35,332 --> 00:14:35,972
Later,

258
00:14:36,692 --> 00:14:38,172
the emperor sent troops

259
00:14:38,692 --> 00:14:40,491
to drive the Earth Fiends underground.

260
00:14:41,572 --> 00:14:43,172
The soldiers who stayed

261
00:14:43,812 --> 00:14:45,611
abandoned their identities

262
00:14:45,891 --> 00:14:47,692
and called themselves
South Mountain Hunters.

263
00:14:47,692 --> 00:14:49,292
and swore enmity with Earth Fiends.

264
00:14:49,452 --> 00:14:50,731
This legacy continues today.

265
00:14:53,812 --> 00:14:55,011
Such detailed settings?

266
00:14:55,212 --> 00:14:56,572
Not writing a novel wastes them.

267
00:14:56,692 --> 00:14:57,851
I've said my piece.

268
00:14:58,651 --> 00:14:59,731
Believe what you will.

269
00:15:01,611 --> 00:15:02,212
Go on.

270
00:15:03,251 --> 00:15:04,572
Those injured by Earth Fiends

271
00:15:04,932 --> 00:15:06,092
develop filmy tissue

272
00:15:06,371 --> 00:15:08,371
over wounds after some time,

273
00:15:08,812 --> 00:15:10,011
like rooting and sprouting.

274
00:15:10,771 --> 00:15:12,412
Though revealing this to an outsider

275
00:15:12,771 --> 00:15:13,651
breaks our rules,

276
00:15:14,172 --> 00:15:15,531
soon I'll also be an outsider.

277
00:15:15,531 --> 00:15:16,332
It doesn't matter.

278
00:15:17,572 --> 00:15:18,371
Besides,

279
00:15:19,131 --> 00:15:20,172
what I described earlier

280
00:15:20,172 --> 00:15:21,611
were beast-like Earth Fiends.

281
00:15:22,491 --> 00:15:24,651
Humanoid ones might differ entirely.

282
00:15:25,172 --> 00:15:26,011
So

283
00:15:26,692 --> 00:15:28,651
you're also a South Mountain Hunter,

284
