and I'll grant you one in return.

570
00:37:09,732 --> 00:37:10,651
I pay each time.

571
00:37:10,972 --> 00:37:11,972
Why so calculative?

572
00:37:12,091 --> 00:37:13,011
Because I don't want

573
00:37:13,011 --> 00:37:14,211
to get entangled with you.

574
00:37:14,691 --> 00:37:16,131
Fine, as you say.

575
00:37:16,372 --> 00:37:17,332
Have you decided?

576
00:37:18,571 --> 00:37:19,932
What's your request this time?

577
00:37:22,611 --> 00:37:23,372
I've decided.

578
00:37:23,772 --> 00:37:25,571
Add me on WeChat. Scan my code.

579
00:37:31,571 --> 00:37:33,051
What brings you here today?

580
00:37:34,171 --> 00:37:36,772
I tried a braised dish spot
last night and found it good.

581
00:37:37,091 --> 00:37:38,452
The owner said they do breakfast,

582
00:37:38,452 --> 00:37:40,651
so I woke early to get you some.

583
00:37:41,252 --> 00:37:41,972
Try it first.

584
00:37:42,171 --> 00:37:43,091
I haven't tried it.

585
00:37:43,372 --> 00:37:45,091
Don't expect too much.
It might disappoint.

586
00:37:48,292 --> 00:37:49,131
Not bad.

587
00:37:49,372 --> 00:37:50,131
It's good?

588
00:37:50,491 --> 00:37:51,452
I'll buy more next time.

589
00:37:56,531 --> 00:37:59,051
I saw the report.
Our business are thriving.

590
00:37:59,611 --> 00:38:00,892
Don't just see the surface.

591
00:38:01,051 --> 00:38:02,252
Such a large group

592
00:38:02,412 --> 00:38:05,292
has countless trivial matters
beneath your notice.

593
00:38:05,732 --> 00:38:07,011
Don't focus only on now either.

594
00:38:07,292 --> 00:38:09,211
The future remains uncertain.

595
00:38:10,051 --> 00:38:11,491
If Roadsound's competitors

596
00:38:11,611 --> 00:38:13,651
had half your crisis awareness,

597
00:38:13,772 --> 00:38:15,611
they wouldn't have stayed
underfoot forever.

598
00:38:17,091 --> 00:38:19,651
You think these internal
and external troubles are imaginary?

599
00:38:21,892 --> 00:38:23,091
That's why I brought breakfast

600
00:38:23,292 --> 00:38:24,332
to ease your mind.

601
00:38:27,412 --> 00:38:28,491
I heard the other day

602
00:38:29,171 --> 00:38:30,252
Xiong caught someone.

603
00:38:30,252 --> 00:38:31,011
What happened?

604
00:38:37,531 --> 00:38:39,892
I know you want to help me,

605
00:38:40,211 --> 00:38:41,892
but some grassroots matters

606
00:38:42,171 --> 00:38:43,772
are better left untouched.

607
00:38:43,852 --> 00:38:44,611
Understood.

608
00:38:48,491 --> 00:38:49,812
The schedule is tight today.

609
00:38:50,211 --> 00:38:52,452
I need to visit the farm
before heading to the office.

610
00:38:53,651 --> 00:38:55,332
You even personally
oversee the planting?

611
00:38:55,611 --> 00:38:57,452
I need to check. I can't rest easy.

612
00:39:26,091 --> 00:39:27,732
Anyone here?

613
00:39:48,611 --> 00:39:51,972
Speak up now if you want less suffering.

614
00:39:55,531 --> 00:39:56,812
I'm old.

615
00:39:57,412 --> 00:39:58,452
I can't handle turmoil.

616
00:39:58,772 --> 00:39:59,772
Let's talk civilly.

617
00:40:03,051 --> 00:40:04,852
Where's the base
of South Mountain Hunters?

618
00:40:05,131 --> 00:40:06,171
How many members in total?

619
00:40:06,892 --> 00:40:08,972
What's your next action plan?

620
00:40:10,292 --> 00:40:11,011
The base...

621
00:40:12,292 --> 00:40:14,292
The base is at the South Heavenly Gate.

622
00:40:15,211 --> 00:40:18,691
Their numbers are hundreds of thousands,
and they are from a celestial army.

623
00:40:19,372 --> 00:40:23,292
And they plan to descend
to eradicate demons and monsters.

624
00:40:28,211 --> 00:40:29,372
Bad with essay questions?

625
00:40:29,852 --> 00:40:31,332
Then we'll make it multiple choice.

626
00:40:32,651 --> 00:40:33,732
How do you want to die?

627
00:40:34,412 --> 00:40:36,332
Bleed out? Heart extraction?

628
00:40:36,651 --> 00:40:38,011
Or live burial?

629
00:40:38,372 --> 00:40:40,812
If you'd brought Mrs. Hua with you,

630
00:40:41,412 --> 00:40:43,051
I'd choose live burial.

631
00:40:44,211 --> 00:40:46,131
We couldn't be together in life.

632
00:40:46,531 --> 00:40:47,932
Sharing a grave in death

633
00:40:48,051 --> 00:40:50,091
would fulfill my wish.

634
00:40:50,332 --> 00:40:51,972
That woman in the hospital

635
00:40:52,651 --> 00:40:53,611
is in such bad shape.

636
00:40:54,772 --> 00:40:56,892
She'll never speak again.

637
00:41:10,211 --> 00:41:11,531
He's quite spirited.

638
00:41:13,171 --> 00:41:14,252
Calm him down.

639
00:41:25,852 --> 00:41:26,812
Long time no see.

640
00:41:26,892 --> 00:41:28,211
Who are you?

641
00:41:29,372 --> 00:41:30,491
Twenty years ago,

642
00:41:30,932 --> 00:41:31,772
I offended you.

643
00:41:32,932 --> 00:41:33,732
Who?

644
00:41:36,611 --> 00:41:38,372
Don't tell me you're holding a grudge,

645
00:41:39,732 --> 00:41:41,732
wanting me to repay you with a leg?

646
00:41:55,400 --> 00:42:01,343
(Greenhouse)

647
00:42:12,372 --> 00:42:14,292
Don't be fooled
by his usual carefree demeanor.

648
00:42:14,812 --> 00:42:16,772
He definitely has his own thoughts.

649
00:42:17,171 --> 00:42:18,491
He just buries them well.

650
00:42:19,491 --> 00:42:21,051
It's fine if it's not a deal-breaker.

651
00:42:21,651 --> 00:42:23,011
It's been many years.

652
00:42:23,772 --> 00:42:25,531
This whole mother-and-son-bond act

653
00:42:26,011 --> 00:42:28,091
has to continue, doesn't it?

654
00:42:28,412 --> 00:42:29,531
No matter what,

655
00:42:29,972 --> 00:42:31,892
Yan Tuo is my own son.

656
00:42:33,412 --> 00:42:35,892
Wake the old man below
and resume interrogation.

657
00:42:36,452 --> 00:42:38,452
We must extract information
about the Mad Blade.

658
00:42:38,611 --> 00:42:39,772
Understood. We'll handle it.

659
00:43:00,812 --> 00:43:01,651
(Lin Ling?)

660
00:43:04,011 --> 00:43:04,732
(Lin Ling?)

661
00:43:06,732 --> 00:43:08,171
(Where are you? Come out.)

662
00:43:09,531 --> 00:43:10,332
(Lin Ling.)

663
00:43:12,091 --> 00:43:12,892
(Lin Ling?)

664
00:43:14,972 --> 00:43:16,171
(Come out now.)

665
00:43:16,892 --> 00:43:17,852
(This is not fun.)

666
00:43:17,932 --> 00:43:19,611
(Ms. Lin will scold us
if she finds out.)

667
00:43:22,252 --> 00:43:23,011
(Lin Ling?)

668
00:43:23,691 --> 00:43:24,452
(Lin Ling?)

669
00:43:27,292 --> 00:43:27,972
(Lin Ling?)

670
00:43:55,976 --> 00:43:58,664
(Toxic and Hazardous)

671
00:44:26,312 --> 00:44:27,200
Lin Xirou.

672
00:44:30,560 --> 00:44:32,880
This humanoid Earth Fiend
and the Roadsound Group

673
00:44:32,920 --> 00:44:34,280
must be closely connected.

674
00:44:34,600 --> 00:44:36,080
This intel is crucial.

675
00:44:36,160 --> 00:44:37,600
We'll investigate immediately.

676
00:44:38,160 --> 00:44:38,800
Thank you.

677
00:44:39,600 --> 00:44:40,640
How's Sun Zhou?

678
00:44:42,440 --> 00:44:43,880
Overcast skies may make us

679
00:44:44,760 --> 00:44:45,720
miss the window.

680
00:44:46,200 --> 00:44:47,120
Do what you can.

681
00:44:47,320 --> 00:44:49,560
If even heaven won't save him,

682
00:44:49,920 --> 00:44:50,880
we can't help with that.

683
00:44:51,400 --> 00:44:52,200
Then

684
00:44:52,520 --> 00:44:54,840
we'll have to banish him to Golden Gate

685
00:44:55,000 --> 00:44:56,160
by Hunters' rules.

686
00:44:57,240 --> 00:44:58,680
Those wounded by Earth Fiends before

687
00:44:58,760 --> 00:45:00,800
and became infected
without timely fire purification

688
00:45:00,880 --> 00:45:02,120
were all Hunters

689
00:45:02,560 --> 00:45:04,040
who vowed to accept this fate.

690
00:45:04,040 --> 00:45:05,240
They were all prepared.

691
00:45:05,560 --> 00:45:07,080
But Sun Zhou is a civilian.

692
00:45:09,640 --> 00:45:10,840
For him,

693
00:45:11,720 --> 00:45:12,800
it's too cruel.

694
00:45:12,808 --> 00:45:13,465
Of course.

695
00:45:14,240 --> 00:45:15,880
I'll explore alternatives.

696
00:45:18,280 --> 00:45:22,600
♪If we don't retreat,
we'll go through it together♪

697
00:45:25,880 --> 00:45:26,800
Are you still there?

698
00:45:27,528 --> 00:45:27,968
Yes.

699
00:45:28,720 --> 00:45:29,680
Speaking of which,

700
00:45:30,400 --> 00:45:32,800
about the informant you mentioned,
who tipped you off

701
00:45:32,960 --> 00:45:34,840
about Lin Xirou and the Roadsound Group,

702
00:45:35,048 --> 00:45:36,090
who is he?

703
00:45:36,600 --> 00:45:37,720
You think he's unreliable?

704
00:45:37,840 --> 00:45:39,520
I'm worried for your safety.

705
00:45:39,720 --> 00:45:41,120
How did you connect with him?

706
00:45:43,240 --> 00:45:44,720
Maybe my unique constitution

707
00:45:44,920 --> 00:45:47,000
attracts oddities.

708
00:45:48,640 --> 00:45:50,520
We've got plenty of oddities here too.

709
00:45:51,360 --> 00:45:54,320
They're all here at the hospital
keeping watch over Mrs. Hua.

710
00:45:54,880 --> 00:45:57,160
I gotta go. It's starting up again.

711
00:45:57,768 --> 00:45:58,284
Okay.

712
00:46:02,904 --> 00:46:07,264
♪The shapeless fire
clings to matter to illuminate♪

713
00:46:07,264 --> 00:46:11,584
♪Yet malice in darkness
defies the flame's pursuit♪

714
00:46:11,584 --> 00:46:16,024
♪A noble name must do righteous deeds♪

715
00:46:16,024 --> 00:46:18,464
♪After sunrise,
even wise words falter in truth♪

716
00:46:18,464 --> 00:46:22,544
♪Heaven-forged fire
scorches flesh and bone♪

717
00:46:22,544 --> 00:46:26,904
♪Dig out the truth buried
beneath the earth♪

718
00:46:26,904 --> 00:46:31,264
♪Heaven-sent tides can't
quench this reckless fire♪

719
00:46:31,264 --> 00:46:35,624
♪If we don't retreat,
we'll go through it together♪

720
00:46:35,624 --> 00:46:39,984
♪Heaven-kindled flames are different♪

721
00:46:39,984 --> 00:46:44,264
♪Truth's madness is hiding
under the surface♪

722
00:46:44,264 --> 00:46:48,824
♪The large waves are rolling
towards the sky♪

723
00:46:48,824 --> 00:46:56,544
♪Farewell to the old times,
and scenes fade away one by one♪

